                                            <div class="title">How fair are we? From conceptualization to automated assessment of fairness definitions</div>
                                            <div class="author">Giordano d’Aloisio, Claudio Di Sipio, Antinisca Di Marco, and Davide Di Ruscio</div>
                                            <div class="periodical">
                                                <em>arXiv preprint arXiv:2404.09919</em>
                                                , 2024
